      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "These are the Past Dunes. Every action here echoes.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "I see footprints… were they here before?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Yes. Someone walked here. In the past.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "So this is where we use Past Simple?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Exactly. For finished actions, long or short.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "We say: I walked. She found. They went.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Do we add -ed?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "For regular verbs, yes: played, watched.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "But some are irregular: go — went, find — found.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "What about questions?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "We use 'did': Did you walk? Did she see?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "And for negatives?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "I didn’t go. He didn’t take.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "I’m ready to try.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
